parameters:
\SE[19]Yay...! I did it! \SE[12]This time the work went
smoothly! \SM[double]\SE[13]I feel like I've improved a
bit...!

\SE[2]Good morning, Vita. \SE[2]I wonder if you were able to
make the shitty game that Laura was talking about?

\SE[12]Good morning...! As expected, you have good
intuition...! \SE[16]This time it's Lunaroa exclusive!
\SM[nod]\SE[13]I'm sure you'll get hooked...!

\SE[13]I named it Lunaroa SLASH!! \!\SE[48]I made it using
only Lunaroa's favorite things!

\SE[12]Lunaroa SLASH!!...!? \!\SE[1]So it's a shitty game
where I'm the protagonist...!

\SE[32]Please, give it a try...! \SE[15]I incorporated the
lessons from last time, so I want to feel everyone's
reactions firsthand...!

\SE[15]Hehe... Such passion... \SE[1]I must approach this
sincerely... It would be rude not to...!

\SE[14]Now, words are unnecessary. Please experience my
shitty game. \!\SE[3]...Oh, is it okay if you waste some
time?

\SE[2]Don't worry about that. \SE[0]I've never felt that the
time spent with you was wasted.

\SE[0]Oh... It's quite elaborate. \SE[0]Is this the
controller that I'll be using to play?

\SE[0]I wonder where we're going...? \!\SE[0]Hehe... I'm
starting to feel a little excited...

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you see. She drinks a lot of water while
studying... so she ends up going to the bathroom... quite
frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
